Package de.hsb.ms.syn.desktop

Starter classes for Desktop host, accessing the main Thesisynth application "Synthesizer".

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DesktopStarter
    Desktop starter class for Thesisynth.
    Synthesizer
    Desktop-sided synthesizer module
    SynthesizerAudioProcessor
    Logic processing unit of the Synthesizer.
    SynthesizerNetworkProcessor
    Net message processor for the SynthesizerProcessor It is notified upon a new NetMessage during the Synthesizer's render() cycle.
    SynthesizerRenderer
    Rendering unit of the Synthesizer.
